data.description: PRICE ADJUSTMENT JUST FOR YOU! Your DREAM HOME is already built! RESORT LIVING! CHECK OUT THIS POOL & CLUBHOUSE! THE SELLERS ARE GRANTING GREAT OPTION PACKAGE to choose from for the buyer! This almost NEW 4 Bedroom 3 FULL bath home built in 2020,  features an open floor plan to entertain guests and allow your creativity to make it your own. The kitchen on the right features granite countertops, middle prep island, stainless steel appliances and breakfast bar seating with additional pantry . The primary suite is tucked in the rear of the home offering plenty of privacy and features a spacious walk-in closet and shower.  Bedroom 2 & 3 are located in the front and the 4th bedroom is nestled in the middle making it a triple split layout for everyone to have their own space. Located on a nice lot with fenced in backyard with Automatic Irrigation! Transferrable Energy Saving Features, abound with Low Utilities. Just bring your furniture and belongings to make this HOME! Whether you're looking to swim, soak up the sun, or simply enjoy the company of neighbors, the community cabana pool area is sure to become your favorite hangout spot. RESORT LIVING all year round! There is a DOG PARK and PICNIC AREA too. Close to Central Florida attractions, shopping and medical facilities. Call today and take a SPOTLIGHT TOUR!
